            </ul>
            <h4>What This Upgrade Does:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Assigns companymanager system role to ALL existing IOMAD company managers</li>
                <li>Enables the companymanager role at system level if not already enabled</li>
                <li>Company search bar works immediately without cache purge</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
    </update>
</updates>
